{"tid":838291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網攻瑞典外交部、電視台　陸網軍：不可能以德報怨","createTime":"2018-09-27T04:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T11:45:29.000Z","uid":75969,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d63bf08aee9ccf3329dc8c05ff5d09ad71bba2c0","tid":838291,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180927/640_8ea225dfb18a1b5d7095a332c648064c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180927%2F640_8ea225dfb18a1b5d7095a332c648064c.jpg&h=6f86af48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國網軍發動對瑞典外交部和電視台的網攻行動。翻攝新浪網</span><br />\n<br />\n中國大陸網友為了報復瑞典電視台製作辱中節目，日前針對瑞典外交部和電視台發起網攻行動。發起網攻的「帝吧」管理員最近受訪表示，中國人無法理解瑞典幽默，也無法「以德報怨」放下此事。<br />\n <br />\n《新京報》報導，大陸人氣貼吧「帝吧」本月24日發起「出征」行動。瑞典外交部、製作諷刺節目的SVT電視台和節目主持人羅恩達爾（Jesper R&ouml;nndahl）的社群網站評論區全被中國網軍「攻陷」。其中羅恩達爾（Jesper R&ouml;nndahl）的臉書成為重災區，其中一篇發文有超過逾1.2萬則留言洗版。<br />\n <br />\n「帝吧」管理員尹先生向《新京報》表示，無法理解瑞典自以為幽默的表達方式：「他們能理解（的幽默），不代表其他國家就能理解啊。尤其是我們中國人一看，你這個針對我們嘛，針對性的嘛。而且（瑞典電視臺）還調侃，還以自以為幽默的方式去表達一些現象。那不能怪我們中國人看不懂啊。」<br />\n <br />\n尹先生說，他們不可能展現「以德報怨」的美德：「所謂的以德報怨嗎？不可能，你還是要表達自己的想法嘛。」另一名參加「帝吧出征」的網友說，他們向來以「聲勢」取勝：「你看不懂中文？但架不住我們人多啊，要的就是那個刷屏的勁兒。」<br />\n <br />\n「愛國」色彩濃厚的「帝吧」網軍曾多次針對外國政府或企業發動網攻，先前曾灌爆在房間放置「否認南京大屠殺」書籍的日本APA連鎖飯店官網，也曾於2016年圍剿總統蔡英文的臉書。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180927/640_5b973715842e1a4c2ba20221c9a7d9d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180927%2F640_5b973715842e1a4c2ba20221c9a7d9d3.jpg&h=488e7c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180927/640_8866ccf27b7d52c12e27d4e84f112c37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180927%2F640_8866ccf27b7d52c12e27d4e84f112c37.jpg&h=3191f500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180927/640_863a65b12f0a28dfce7abea8876f0ee5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180927%2F640_863a65b12f0a28dfce7abea8876f0ee5.jpg&h=e4d0f405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180927/1437122/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180927%2F1437122%2F&d=2ZXDsFvQquetjzfk29FMlYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=77217a6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180927%2F1437122%2F&h=c52a1a1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180927/1437122/</a>"},{"pid":"ba2cb62066705b0a196603e113ce9a2c67a06c66","tid":838291,"uid":25659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:17:33.000Z","msg":"好柒呀班支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157e071399ee6fef9659b57238358caf6cbb3085","tid":838291,"uid":37413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:18:07.000Z","msg":"請問， 人哋有冇少一條毛？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46292c7759417915b69c169b948472f1196cc087","tid":838291,"uid":144626,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"中國人都無德，何來以德報怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae968e0df3b70028ab5677fc0ca83b340980ece","tid":838291,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"支那 = 垃圾"},{"pid":"af0ebeb27977528d964b4f19eb8919fb35ca8ef6","tid":838291,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:23:27.000Z","msg":"google translate <img 